\par
\tab The Information Technology Act, 2000: The Information Technology Act, 2000, includes provisions related to unauthorized access to computer systems, data theft, and cyberstalking. Lori Drew could be charged with violating the IT Act if she gained unauthorized access to Megan's computer system to create the fake MySpace profile.\par
\par
\fs28 Conclusion\fs24 :\par
