\par
\tab The Information Technology Act, 2000: The Information Technology Act, 2000, includes provisions related to hacking, identity theft, and phishing. The scammers could be charged with phishing for using fraudulent emails to trick the victim into sharing her personal information.\par
\par
\fs28 Conclusion\fs24 :\par
